                        <div class="cognitive-icon"><img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,cognitive-services,face.png"/></div>
                        <div class="cognitive-text">
                            <h2>人脸识别 API</h2>
                            <p>检测图片中人脸位置，依照视觉相似度做人脸比对、分组、以及辨识由用户标记过身份的人脸。</p>
                            <p><a id="cognitive-services_face" href="/home/features/cognitive-services/face/" class="single-link">了解更多<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>                    
                    <li>
